snippet.title: art of rally - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/550320/art_of_rally/
Wishlist on GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/art_of_rally
Website: http://artofrally.com/
Discord: https://discord.gg/kcVbHR9

The new racing game from the creator of Absolute Drift! 

Race in the golden era of rally. Drive 50+ iconic cars from the 60s to 90s on challenging stages through stylized environments like Finland, Norway and Japan. Will you master the art of rally?


Trailer created by Nassault: https://www.youtube.com/user/Nassault630
